1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the language developed by agents in emergent-communication settings.
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with the development of communication systems by agents.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the evolving interaction between agents and the representations they develop.
4. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper considers the visual input and representations developed by the agents.
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also relevant as the paper discusses the use of neural networks in the referential games.
